data.description: ***PRICE IMPROVEMENT**** Discover this hidden gem at the heart of Port Charlotte. This charming home located on a big corner lot and at higher elevation than others homes near by. Across the street form canal homes. This home is a 2 bedroom, 1 bath with luxury vinyl flooring throughout, new roof just replaced, newer a/c. Includes fruit trees such as; Haus avocado, mango, citrus trees such as, lemon, lime and oranges. Egg producing chickens with small chicken coup. Planter Boxes that are held to the ground. Removable garden boxes on all front windows. Huge yard fully fenced with a brand new white vinyl fence. Located close to Charlotte Harbor where the Peace River meets the Gulf, within minutes to the new Sunseeker Resort development. This is your opportunity to live where others vacation! Great as second home or investment  property.
